extends layout

block content
    .container.mt-5

        .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-9

                .card.border-0.shadow-lg
                    .card-body.p-5

                        h2.mb-4 Privacy Policy

                        p.text-muted
                            | Your privacy matters to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

                        hr

                        h5.mt-4 Information We Collect
                        p.text-muted
                            | We collect basic account details such as your name and email, as well as activity data like listings, requests, and interactions.

                        h5.mt-4 How We Use Your Data
                        p.text-muted
                            | Your data is used to provide our services, connect users, improve the platform, and maintain security.

                        h5.mt-4 Data Protection
                        p.text-muted
                            | We do not sell your personal data. All information is handled securely and responsibly.

                        h5.mt-4 Your Rights
                        p.text-muted
                            | You have the right to access, update, or request deletion of your data at any time.

                        h5.mt-4 Contact
                        p.text-muted.mb-0
                            | For any privacy-related concerns, contact us at 
                            | strong privacy@shareloop.com